{"tid":1323780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Black Bloc] 重要！保護自己及同路人！","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T02:58:47.000Z","uid":215706,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"45f3f644224f16c73037620edf56d9182412634b","tid":1323780,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"Black Bloc 保護緊嘅唔只係你自己一個<br />\n仲有成千上萬嘅同路人 唔係想做打手<br />\n但請大家互相為大家安全著想 保護大家<br />\n參與接下來嘅遊行前 花少少時間去買以下呢堆裝備<br />\n取材自Decathlon 迪卡儂 價錢算係抵到爛<br />\n將軍澳 旺角 銅鑼灣 都有分店<br />\n<br />\n1. 上衣 <br />\na. 黑色T shirt $24<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1073980/k$8c1655cbc11f4a3994a3a2eb2ef867ba/sq/.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1073980%2Fk%248c1655cbc11f4a3994a3a2eb2ef867ba%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=4542058c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nb. 黑色連帽衛衣 $129 <br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1419373/k$960549548576b4a7586cf10e36bcaf10/sq/.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1419373%2Fk%24960549548576b4a7586cf10e36bcaf10%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=42321015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nc. 黑色防水風褸 $149<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1609841/k$05437b8660c181807a139b202cd78982/sq/T100.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1609841%2Fk%2405437b8660c181807a139b202cd78982%2Fsq%2FT100.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=2e18a845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 下身<br />\n<br />\na. 黑色網球長褲 $69<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1250319/k$7cb3dcd51b4a251f06ea090d5cdf991b/sq/.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1250319%2Fk%247cb3dcd51b4a251f06ea090d5cdf991b%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=8ecd6499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nb. 黑色耐磨狩獵褲 $159<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p298255/k$e8f7eea4f12af3b78b529dc7a0923f11/sq/Steppe+300.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp298255%2Fk%24e8f7eea4f12af3b78b529dc7a0923f11%2Fsq%2FSteppe%2B300.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=1dceda67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 帽<br />\n<br />\na. 黑色透氣cap帽 $49<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1586129/k$18bb012c60da12297a91bd188d3bd213/sq/.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1586129%2Fk%2418bb012c60da12297a91bd188d3bd213%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=126c7cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nb. 黑色防曬cap帽 $49<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1329866/k$62a5cf567206d79817113ce57716fe8f/sq/.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1329866%2Fk%2462a5cf567206d79817113ce57716fe8f%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=838af7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 面罩/遮樣面巾<br />\n<br />\na. 灰色多功能頭/頸帶 $19<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1070278/k$0f64453a7c760e47a6021ef23b48c0f0/sq/.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1070278%2Fk%240f64453a7c760e47a6021ef23b48c0f0%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=b5cb18c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nb. 買多件上面1a $24<br />\n再依照下面呢張圖黎綁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnCGK1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnCGK1F.jpg&h=eb0189ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 鞋<br />\n<br />\na. 綁帶版白飯魚 <br />\n一定要係綁帶款因為冇咁易甩<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBTbcLt.img?h=416&amp;w=624&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBTbcLt.img%3Fh%3D416%26w%3D624%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=aeeecea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nb. 黑色運動訓練鞋 $129<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1560767/k$c0c56281c2c8497c61240f723a7d67fc/sq/.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1560767%2Fk%24c0c56281c2c8497c61240f723a7d67fc%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=efb027a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 防具 (口罩眼罩頭盔等)<br />\n自己去樓下五金舖買 唔好去到現場先問物資站拎<br />\n物資站同前綫其實好大壓力 特別係防具<br />\n<br />\n7. 工具 (索帶士巴拿等)<br />\n都係自己去樓下五金舖買<br />\n士巴拿可參考下面做法自己整<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cmoneyhome.com/article/6370/%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%B8%AB%E7%88%B6%E7%A7%98%E6%8A%80!%20%E7%84%A1%E5%A3%AB%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E9%83%BD%E8%83%BD%E6%89%AD%E5%88%B0%E5%85%AD%E8%A7%92%E8%9E%BA%E7%B5%B2%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmoneyhome.com%2Farticle%2F6370%2F%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2588%25B6%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%258A%2580%21%2520%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%258B%25BF%25E9%2583%25BD%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2589%25AD%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%259E%25BA%25E7%25B5%25B2%25EF%25BC%2581&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTebtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=f6acccad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cmoneyhome.com/article/6370/%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE%E5%B8%AB%E7%88%B6%E7%A7%98%E6%8A%80!%20%E7%84%A1%E5%A3%AB%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E9%83%BD%E8%83%BD%E6%89%AD%E5%88%B0%E5%85%AD%E8%A7%92%E8%9E%BA%E7%B5%B2%EF%BC%81</a><br />\n<br />\n8. 其他配件<br />\n<br />\na. 黑色輕巧背囊 $19<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1161458/k$f64261cd232cb02ef8102b34cc75d2cd/sq/Travel+10+L.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1161458%2Fk%24f64261cd232cb02ef8102b34cc75d2cd%2Fsq%2FTravel%2B10%2BL.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=07efc1c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nb. 黑色太陽眼鏡 $29<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1251800/k$a98ac92a95d537237918f5de7b13c23c/sq/ST+100+MTB+3.webp?f=550x550\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1251800%2Fk%24a98ac92a95d537237918f5de7b13c23c%2Fsq%2FST%2B100%2BMTB%2B3.webp%3Ff%3D550x550&h=5e450ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面嘅野 簡簡單單買一套比自己<br />\n保護自己於人群中 同時亦保護其他人群入面嘅戰友<br />\n加加埋埋都係500蚊左右<br />\n大家21 28號前記住記住記住去買一套<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e53e49e849f65df6db9121f1d62434fffc3f74","tid":1323780,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:05:55.000Z","msg":"二連"},{"pid":"6641e376d0b18c9c742c1e240803d0c856378cec","tid":1323780,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"三連"},{"pid":"684701c57b5ff0de5952fb2a658fe448f730660e","tid":1323780,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"四連"},{"pid":"6edc0b2a843a0ffa50d0fbe3da685ded57100dee","tid":1323780,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"五連"},{"pid":"301178c8c9c5d4ca46bfdc4ba8f95ffef7872897","tid":1323780,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"六連"},{"pid":"3c265c90b7c367cdb64156837867b2763d3c84b4","tid":1323780,"uid":215706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:06:47